title: Desirable North Everett Home, Huge Double Lot. Avail Sept 1st.
posting_body: ['*****open house sat Aug 6th 10am to 1pm.', ' This will be the only time to view the house and apply.', 'Do not miss out!*****2br/1bath 1200sq home with large open kithen and living space.', 'Hardwood floors on main floor and master bedroom.', 'Laundy room on main floor (washer/dryer stays).', 'Huge daylight basement perfect for hobbies and storage.', 'French doors open to large deck, perfect for entertaining.', 'Home is on a double lot with large grassy area for your kids to play.', 'Storage shed on property good for lawn equipment.', 'Parking available through alley in back of the home.', 'Whittier/North/Everett high schools.', 'Wonderful neighborhood, good parks, within 1 mile of downtown Everett.', 'Home is a short 15 minute commute to Boeing.', 'THERE IS A NON REFUNDABLE APPLICATION FEE FOR BACKGROUND AND CREDIT CHECKS', 'Basic terms of Lease : 1st and last month rent plus 500 damage/security deposit.', '750 deposit if you have pets.', 'Renter pays all utilities and is responsible for lawncare .', 'Application fee non refundable.', '1st and last month, 500 deposit plus 250 for pets..', 'Min credit score of 680.']
